<aka>mạ ạ̉ʿjb ạtḍạʿk yạ rbnạ ạlmjyd</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mā ạảʿ̊jaba ạtĩḍāʿaka
 yā rabãnā ạl̊majīd̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ qad̊ ẓahar̊ta biạl̊jasad̊
 fī ṣūraẗi ạl̊ʿabīd̊

[V2]
 2- wāản̊ta makẖ̊dūmuⁿ mina
 ạlạảm̊lạki wāl̊junūd̊
 narāka qad̊ kẖadam̊tanā
 fī ạlạảr̊ḍi yā wadūd̊

[V3]
 3- fāldãm̊ʿa qad̊ sakab̊tahu
 yā rabãnā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 wāldãma qad̊ safak̊tahu
 ʿanãạ ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V4]
 4- wāl̊maẘta qad̊ qabil̊tahu
 yā rabũ dẖā ạlại̹n̊ʿām̊
 wāl̊kẖaẘfa qad̊ ạảb̊dal̊tahu
 ṣul̊ḥaⁿạ kadẖā salạm̊

[V5]
 5- tẖumã litalạmīdẖika
 ḥaḍar̊ta yā ḥanūn̊
 yadaẙka qad̊ ạảraẙtahum̊
 wajan̊baka ạl̊maṭ̊ʿūn̊

[V6]
 6- walam̊ tazal̊ turī
 jirāḥaka ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊
 wanaḥ̊nu daẘmaⁿạ naṣ̊naʿu
 dẖik̊rāka yā ḥabīb̊

[V7]
 7- fāl̊qal̊bu mad̊yūnuⁿ biạản̊
 yasẖ̊dū bikẖid̊matik̊
 wāl̊famu daẘmaⁿạ yasẖ̊kuru
 ạảf̊ḍāla niʿ̊matik̊</lyrics>
<title>mạ ạ̉ʿjb ạtḍạʿk</title>
</song>